  3.629277335547448*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"90343475-10c5-4732-8698-\
e7b302dcbcc7"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Signal may be converted into the frequency-domain and plotted using the \
Fourier transform operation ",
 StyleBox["FT. ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "The result is a set of {frequency, amplitude} pairs, where the frequency \
coordinates are here in Hz:"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.629276957909128*^9, 
  3.6292770528585377`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"14769a91-0a48-4a92-a45e-\
3d51818279cd"],

