Cell["\<\
A more accurate spectral representation is generated by adding zeroes to \
increase the data length by a factor of 8 before Fourier transformation:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.629279044784832*^9, 
  3.629279138731834*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"73b3a1a8-4c48-420c-86be-\
